    <title>Opencv的环境配置</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2025/10/16/opencv%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2025/10/16/opencv%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA/</id>
    <published>2025-10-16T08:48:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-10-16T10:07:44.930Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="在Anaconda中下载安装opencv"><a href="#在Anaconda中下载安装opencv" class="headerlink" title="在Anaconda中下载安装opencv"></a>在Anaconda中下载安装opencv</h1><p>1.Anaconda的下载参照前文“Python的安装”<br>2.首先打开我们的终端，当前在Windows系统中操作，还是熟悉的win+R-&gt;cmd<br>3.跳转到Anaconda的文件(以你的实际路径为准)</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">D:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> Anaconda</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.输入python可查看当前python版本，避免后续下载过程中的兼容问题，输入exit()退出。<br>5.可以直接下载,如果后面不添加&#x3D;&#x3D;3.4.1.15（具体版本号）,则默认下载最新版，下载具体版本时注意版本兼容问题。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> Scripts</span><br><span class="line">pip install opencv-python</span><br><span class="line">pip install opencv-contrib-python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5.查看当前已下载的目录，检查是否下载成功</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6.打开python进行检查</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> cv2</span><br><span class="line">cv2.__version__</span><br><span class="line">exit()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现版本信息则证明安装成功</p><h1 id="在PyCharm中进行简单的图像的初步处理"><a href="#在PyCharm中进行简单的图像的初步处理" class="headerlink" title="在PyCharm中进行简单的图像的初步处理"></a>在PyCharm中进行简单的图像的初步处理</h1><p>1.PyCharm的下载参照前文“Python的安装”<br>2.在PyCharm中创建一个新文件，选择自定义环境，如果有多个python版本请注意路径与之前Anaconda下载安装opencv的路径一致。<br>3.在与新建文件的同一个根目录下加入图片，如：</p><!--猫猫 --><p><img src="/uploads/cat.jpg" alt="cat"><br>4.输入以下代码尝试是否运行成功</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> cv2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 读取图像（参数1：路径，参数2：读取模式）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cv2.IMREAD_COLOR：默认，读取彩色图像（忽略透明度）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cv2.IMREAD_GRAYSCALE：读取为灰度图</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cv2.IMREAD_UNCHANGED：读取完整图像（包括透明度）</span></span><br><span class="line">img = cv2.imread(<span class="string">&quot;cat.jpg&quot;</span>, cv2.IMREAD_COLOR)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查图像是否读取成功</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> img <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">None</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;无法读取图像，请检查路径是否正确&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;图像形状：<span class="subst">&#123;img.shape&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)  <span class="comment"># (高度, 宽度, 通道数)，彩色图通道数为3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 显示图像（参数1：窗口名，参数2：图像数据）</span></span><br><span class="line">cv2.imshow(<span class="string">&quot;Original Image&quot;</span>, img)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 等待用户按键（参数为毫秒数，0表示无限等待）</span></span><br><span class="line">cv2.waitKey(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 关闭所有OpenCV窗口</span></span><br><span class="line">cv2.destroyAllWindows()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># BGR转RGB（matplotlib显示时需要）</span></span><br><span class="line">img_rgb = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># BGR转灰度图（减少计算量，常用于后续处理）</span></span><br><span class="line">img_gray = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.imshow(<span class="string">&quot;Gray Image&quot;</span>, img_gray)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.waitKey(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.destroyAllWindows()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 方法1：指定目标宽度和高度</span></span><br><span class="line">width, height = <span class="number">300</span>, <span class="number">200</span>  <span class="comment"># 新尺寸（宽, 高）</span></span><br><span class="line">img_resized = cv2.resize(img, (width, height))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 方法2：按比例缩放（例如缩小为原来的50%）</span></span><br><span class="line">scale = <span class="number">0.5</span></span><br><span class="line">img_scaled = cv2.resize(img, <span class="literal">None</span>, fx=scale, fy=scale)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cv2.imshow(<span class="string">&quot;Resized Image&quot;</span>, img_resized)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.waitKey(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.destroyAllWindows()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 保存图像（参数1：保存路径，参数2：图像数据）</span></span><br><span class="line">cv2.imwrite(<span class="string">&quot;processed_image.jpg&quot;</span>, img_resized)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;图像保存成功&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="后续更新"><a href="#后续更新" class="headerlink" title="后续更新"></a>后续更新</h1><p>在搭建好环境以及学会简单的图片处理以后，接下来，我们将会学习视频的处理（视频的初步处理本质是对视频帧（每一帧都是一幅图像） 的连续处理，也就是处理图像。），再由本地视频过渡到实时监控，进而服务于实际运用。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
