    <title>Python初学</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2025/09/14/Python%E5%88%9D%E5%AD%A6/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2025/09/14/Python%E5%88%9D%E5%AD%A6/</id>
    <published>2025-09-14T11:00:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-10-16T09:01:24.766Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="从”HelloWord”开始"><a href="#从”HelloWord”开始" class="headerlink" title="从”HelloWord”开始"></a>从”HelloWord”开始</h1><p>在C语言中，printf函数需要引入标准输入输出库，以main函数作为程序入口，示例代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span>  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World!\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Python则更为简洁：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="列表、元组、字典、集合"><a href="#列表、元组、字典、集合" class="headerlink" title="列表、元组、字典、集合"></a>列表、元组、字典、集合</h1><h2 id="1-核心特点"><a href="#1-核心特点" class="headerlink" title="1.核心特点"></a>1.核心特点</h2><p>Python 中列表、元组、字典、集合是常用的内置数据结构，核心特点如下：<br>列表 (list) []有序、可变、可重复，支持索引、切片操作<br>元组 (Tuple) ()有序、不可变、可重复，比列表节省内存<br>字典 (Dictionary) {:}无序，键不可变、不可重复，查询效率高<br>集合 (Set) {} &#x2F;set ()无序、可变、不可重复，支持交、并集等操作<br>（补充说明：字典的 “不可变 &#x2F; 不可重复” 是针对键而言，值可修改；集合支持交、并、差等集合运算。）</p><h2 id="2-细节理解"><a href="#2-细节理解" class="headerlink" title="2.细节理解"></a>2.细节理解</h2><h3 id="（1）列表的简单运用"><a href="#（1）列表的简单运用" class="headerlink" title="（1）列表的简单运用"></a>（1）列表的简单运用</h3><p>接下来，让我们从具体题目中理解：</p><p>链接：<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/two-sum/description/">两数之和</a><br>我们以比较简单的，时间复杂度为O(n^2)的方法为例。<br>假设这两个数一个为a,一个为b。我们对数组进行依次遍历，假设遍历的每一个数为a,那么我们只需判断target-a是否在数组里并返回下标就好了。关于下标，可以运用列表的 index() 方法。<br>nums.index(value)：列表的 index(）方法，用于查找 value在 nums中首次出现的索引（即位置，从 0 开始计数）。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将输入的字符串分割为多个子串，转换为整数后组成列表</span></span><br><span class="line"> nums = <span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="built_in">map</span>(<span class="built_in">int</span>, <span class="built_in">input</span>().split())) </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment"># 读取目标和值，并转换为整数类型 </span></span><br><span class="line"> target = <span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>()) </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment"># 获取列表nums的长度 </span></span><br><span class="line"> n = <span class="built_in">len</span>(nums) </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment"># 遍历列表中的每个元素的索引 </span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(n):     </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 获取当前索引对应的元素值     </span></span><br><span class="line">    x = nums[i]     </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 判断补数是否在列表中且索引不同     </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> target - x <span class="keyword">in</span> nums <span class="keyword">and</span> i != nums.index(target - x):         </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 记录补数的索引         </span></span><br><span class="line">        b = nums.index(target - x)         </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 记录当前元素的索引         </span></span><br><span class="line">        a = i; <span class="comment"># 输出结果 </span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;[<span class="subst">&#123;b&#125;</span>,<span class="subst">&#123;a&#125;</span>]&quot;</span>) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行结果：</p><h3 id="（2）列表的切片操作"><a href="#（2）列表的切片操作" class="headerlink" title="（2）列表的切片操作"></a>（2）列表的切片操作</h3><p>如何优化呢？<br>我们注意到，在这个方法中，a遍历找到b后，循环没有停止，b（假设b是在a后面遍历）还会再遍历找到a,我们当然可以用break来阻止重复循环的发生，但是，还可利用切片操作来达到目的。<br>也就是说，我们可以只在a的后面中遍历寻找b，那么b就不必再找一次a。那么nums.index(target - x)就变为nums[i+1:].index(target - x)+i+1<br>具体代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nums=<span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="built_in">map</span>(<span class="built_in">int</span>,<span class="built_in">input</span>().split())) </span><br><span class="line">target=<span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>()) n=<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums) </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(n):     </span><br><span class="line">    x=nums[i]     </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> target-x <span class="keyword">in</span> nums[i+<span class="number">1</span>:] :         </span><br><span class="line">        b =nums[i+<span class="number">1</span>:].index(target - x)+i+<span class="number">1</span>         </span><br><span class="line">        a=i; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;[<span class="subst">&#123;a&#125;</span>,<span class="subst">&#123;b&#125;</span>]&quot;</span>) </span><br><span class="line">运行结果：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">### (3)元组与字典</span></span><br><span class="line">还可以优化吗？当然</span><br><span class="line">我们注意到字典查询效率高的特点，是否能把值与下标转化为字典呢？</span><br><span class="line">这里我将介绍一个<span class="built_in">enumerate</span>()函数。</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(nums)返回的不是单个元组，而是一个枚举对象（<span class="built_in">enumerate</span> <span class="built_in">object</span>）—— 它是一种可迭代对象，当你遍历它时，每次迭代会产生一个元组（包含索引和对应的元素）。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">那么<span class="keyword">for</span> index, num <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(nums)：temp[num]=index<span class="comment">#(temp=&#123;&#125;)就可以得到字典了。</span></span><br><span class="line">具体代码如下：</span><br><span class="line">```Python</span><br><span class="line">nums=<span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="built_in">map</span>(<span class="built_in">int</span>,<span class="built_in">input</span>().split())) </span><br><span class="line">target=<span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>()) temp=&#123;&#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i, x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(nums):</span><br><span class="line">    temp[x]=i </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i, x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(nums):     </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> target-x <span class="keyword">in</span> temp <span class="keyword">and</span> temp[target-x]!=i:         </span><br><span class="line">            b =temp[target-x]         </span><br><span class="line">            a=i; </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;[<span class="subst">&#123;b&#125;</span>,<span class="subst">&#123;a&#125;</span>]&quot;</span>) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行结果如下：</p><p>从591ms到4ms，为何提升如此之大？因为：<br>字典（哈希表）的平均查找时间复杂度是 O (1)，而列表的线性查找是 O (n)。第二版代码通过字典将两次 O (n) 的查找操作优化为 O (1)，从而将整体复杂度从 O (n²) 降至 O (n)，因此效率更高。</p><p>当然，在网上的题解里面还有更优的方法，这里我就不一一讲解了。希望对列表、元组、字典、集合的理解有所帮助。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
